			<h4><a id="comment_link_64391302" name="comment_link_64391302" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23289862&amp;cid=64391302" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64391302)" >US auto industry cedes the market again</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64391302" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64391302); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>4</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
