	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64391528">Why not ensure the heavy industry isn't as polluting? The USA still had heavy industry and because of pretty good regulation (EPA, etc) it's not as polluting as in some other countries. That regulation comes at a cost and we should encourage other countries to reduce pollution from heavy industry to help level the playing field and ensure that external costs are internalised into the product. How to achieve that change is another question.</div>
	</div>

